WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.620
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.740
=Episode 2=

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:56.640
If you insist on going,

00:00:57.070 --> 00:00:58.560
once you hear the crows caw,

00:00:58.560 --> 00:00:59.840
be careful of both sides.

00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:00.793
There will be an ambush.

00:01:32.370 --> 00:01:33.230
(Of the ten petals,)

00:01:33.230 --> 00:01:34.870
(only one remains.)

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:37.430
(This is my tenth reincarnation.)

00:01:38.790 --> 00:01:39.870
Jiang Ruoli

00:01:40.790 --> 00:01:41.870
knows the future.

00:01:42.950 --> 00:01:45.040
She must be able to change
the fate of my death.

00:01:46.790 --> 00:01:48.430
What else do you know?

00:01:52.510 --> 00:01:53.350
Mr. Huo,

00:01:53.826 --> 00:01:55.026
today is the Lantern Festival.

00:01:55.150 --> 00:01:57.040
Shall we book a banquet
at Chunman Tavern?

00:01:57.990 --> 00:01:58.820
(Oh, no.)

00:01:58.840 --> 00:01:59.960
(It's the Lantern Festival.)

00:01:59.960 --> 00:02:01.900
(10th lifetime, Lantern Festival)

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:11.840
Stop!

00:02:15.190 --> 00:02:16.030
Stop!

00:02:25.750 --> 00:02:26.590
Hurry!

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:12.520
Who's there?

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:13.710
Capture them alive.

00:03:19.910 --> 00:03:20.750
You...

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:21.920
Who are you?

00:03:22.750 --> 00:03:23.590
Ruoli?

00:05:14.420 --> 00:05:16.020
(Huo Mansion)

00:05:16.040 --> 00:05:16.880
Mr. Huo,

00:05:17.136 --> 00:05:18.823
there are clues
about the man in question.

00:05:20.220 --> 00:05:22.100
(Shitou)

00:05:38.750 --> 00:05:39.590
Yanzhi.

00:05:40.390 --> 00:05:41.230
Huaijin,

00:05:41.800 --> 00:05:42.640
why are you here?

00:05:43.413 --> 00:05:45.700
(Lu Huaijin, Duke's foster son)
I heard about last night.

00:05:45.750 --> 00:05:47.120
You brought Ruoli back.

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:48.766
I wonder how her injuries are.

00:05:50.830 --> 00:05:51.680
When

00:05:52.310 --> 00:05:53.360
did you two meet?

00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:54.560
When we were kids.

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:56.560
I wonder who'd do

00:05:56.720 --> 00:05:58.430
something so vicious.

00:06:02.830 --> 00:06:04.240
I have urgent matters to attend to.

00:06:04.310 --> 00:06:06.040
Please help look after her.

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:20.360
Secretly send people
to protect Miss Jiang.

00:06:20.360 --> 00:06:21.240
Yes.

00:06:37.560 --> 00:06:38.560
Yunzhou.

00:06:39.270 --> 00:06:40.680
Ruoli, you are awake.

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:56.480
Yunzhou,

00:06:57.600 --> 00:06:58.440
where am I?

00:06:58.720 --> 00:06:59.666
This is the Huo Mansion.

00:07:02.040 --> 00:07:02.880
Last night,

00:07:04.070 --> 00:07:06.000
were you the one taking care of me?

00:07:08.510 --> 00:07:09.750
You look very pale.

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:11.190
But don't worry.

00:07:11.560 --> 00:07:12.680
It's safe now.

00:07:17.310 --> 00:07:18.750
Thank you, Yunzhou.

00:07:20.900 --> 00:07:21.750
By the way,

00:07:21.750 --> 00:07:22.600
where are my parents?

00:07:25.750 --> 00:07:26.590
Last night,

00:07:27.160 --> 00:07:28.800
your home was attacked.

00:07:29.430 --> 00:07:30.270
However,

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:31.853
there was no serious harm.

00:07:35.040 --> 00:07:35.920
Help!

00:07:38.310 --> 00:07:39.490
(Was the ending in my dream)

00:07:39.600 --> 00:07:40.870
(really changed?)

00:07:42.140 --> 00:07:44.420
(Jiang Mansion)

00:07:46.270 --> 00:07:49.630
Last night, thanks to Mr. Huo
sending people on time,

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:52.390
your father's life was saved.

00:07:52.830 --> 00:07:54.120
Mr. Huo?

00:07:54.750 --> 00:07:55.590
Yes.

00:07:55.950 --> 00:07:57.630
(He saved my parents?)

00:07:58.830 --> 00:07:59.670
Mother,

00:07:59.920 --> 00:08:01.270
did you catch the murderer?

00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:05.950
Madam, Lady Ruoli,

00:08:05.950 --> 00:08:06.870
bad news.

00:08:06.870 --> 00:08:07.920
Master Huaikang is trying

00:08:07.920 --> 00:08:09.830
(Tao)
to be the patriarch.

00:08:10.310 --> 00:08:11.310
What?

00:08:27.020 --> 00:08:29.900
(Jiang Mansion)

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:34.320
Your uncle

00:08:34.910 --> 00:08:36.000
is now unconscious,

00:08:36.510 --> 00:08:38.320
unable to manage family affairs.

00:08:39.480 --> 00:08:41.790
Still, our family must have a leader.

00:08:42.079 --> 00:08:43.908
At the Si hour,
the ancestral hall will open.

00:08:44.080 --> 00:08:45.720
Even if it means carving out my heart,

00:08:46.030 --> 00:08:48.000
I'll hold up the family.

00:08:49.160 --> 00:08:49.696
Father,

00:08:49.707 --> 00:08:51.707
you've managed external affairs
for over a decade.

00:08:51.718 --> 00:08:52.983
You deserve this responsibility.

00:08:54.270 --> 00:08:55.840
What talk of carving out the heart.

00:08:59.910 --> 00:09:01.440
The stewards haven't arrived yet,

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:03.150
but you are already informed.

00:09:03.840 --> 00:09:05.000
My father lies unconscious.

00:09:05.750 --> 00:09:07.200
Instead of catching the murderer,

00:09:07.910 --> 00:09:10.270
you rush to seize
the patriarch position.

00:09:12.200 --> 00:09:13.750
The main branch has no male heir.

00:09:13.750 --> 00:09:16.790
Do you want to preside over the family?

00:09:18.120 --> 00:09:19.440
As an elder of the family,

00:09:19.840 --> 00:09:21.510
I should take on this responsibility.

00:09:22.030 --> 00:09:22.910
The priority now...

00:09:22.910 --> 00:09:24.240
It's to find the murderer,

00:09:24.616 --> 00:09:26.200
not fighting here for power and profit

00:09:26.200 --> 00:09:27.730
while hoping my father never wakes up.

00:09:30.360 --> 00:09:31.200
Uncle,

00:09:31.960 --> 00:09:33.670
you keep saying it is for the family.

00:09:34.390 --> 00:09:35.230
Then tell me.

00:09:35.720 --> 00:09:37.120
Where were you when the assassins

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.139
- came last night?
- I...

00:09:38.150 --> 00:09:39.030
Why were your guards

00:09:39.030 --> 00:09:39.960
completely unharmed?

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:40.800
You...

00:09:40.800 --> 00:09:42.446
As long as my father
has one breath left,

00:09:43.150 --> 00:09:45.510
the patriarch position
will never fall to another.

00:09:46.550 --> 00:09:47.390
You...

00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:49.390
Jiang Ruoli!

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:51.870
From now on,

00:09:52.750 --> 00:09:54.790
I'll personally guard my parents.

00:09:55.440 --> 00:09:56.750
No one is allowed to approach.

00:09:57.960 --> 00:09:59.000
Anyone who dares

00:09:59.390 --> 00:10:02.030
can't blame me for showing no mercy.

00:10:09.380 --> 00:10:12.140
(Auspices and Blessings)

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:14.080
Did you see that?

00:10:14.440 --> 00:10:15.840
Jiang Ruoli

00:10:16.030 --> 00:10:17.720
was quite imposing today.

00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:20.320
She's lost her backing,

00:10:20.550 --> 00:10:23.120
yet she still dares to ride over me.

00:10:23.440 --> 00:10:26.440
I think she wants to seize power

00:10:26.870 --> 00:10:28.840
and cut off my path to power.

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:31.960
Father, don't be angry.

00:10:32.200 --> 00:10:33.910
Uncle has been seriously injured.

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:36.870
Jiang Ruoli alone can't achieve much.

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:38.510
We will find another opportunity.

00:10:39.240 --> 00:10:40.080
Wanyue,

00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:42.720
our time is running out.

00:10:43.080 --> 00:10:45.120
I've endured humiliation for years.

00:10:45.320 --> 00:10:47.150
With such a good situation,

00:10:47.550 --> 00:10:50.030
we can't watch Jiang Ruoli

00:10:50.030 --> 00:10:51.120
ruin everything.

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:52.960
You are right.

00:10:53.630 --> 00:10:56.120
She's always overshadowed me.

00:10:56.480 --> 00:10:57.720
We can't let this continue.

00:10:58.630 --> 00:11:01.480
Then I'll rely on you.

00:11:09.030 --> 00:11:09.910
Reverie Powder.

00:11:11.360 --> 00:11:12.480
Jiang Ruoli,

00:11:13.080 --> 00:11:15.080
I'll destroy your virginity.

00:11:15.390 --> 00:11:16.910
Let's see how arrogant you can remain.

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:35.480
Milady, your calming medicine.

00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:50.240
Who prepared

00:11:51.120 --> 00:11:51.960
this medicine?

00:11:52.320 --> 00:11:53.840
(Ruyan)
The kitchen gave it to me.

00:11:54.550 --> 00:11:55.480
What is wrong?

00:11:58.303 --> 00:12:00.383
The physician never prescribed
such medicine for me.

00:12:01.480 --> 00:12:02.320
This medicine

00:12:03.600 --> 00:12:04.550
must have a problem.

00:12:07.910 --> 00:12:09.960
(Father lies unconscious.)

00:12:10.840 --> 00:12:13.200
(Mother and I are
in an increasingly hard position.)

00:12:14.030 --> 00:12:15.720
(I must come up with a foolproof plan.)

00:12:17.180 --> 00:12:19.740
(Jiang Mansion)

00:12:34.910 --> 00:12:36.360
Something's wrong with the incense.

00:12:42.630 --> 00:12:43.480
Tao.

00:12:44.270 --> 00:12:45.240
Ruyan.

00:12:47.120 --> 00:12:48.510
(I knew you were not that stupid.)

00:12:48.510 --> 00:12:50.000
(So, I prepared another move.)

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:50.840
Milady.

00:12:51.910 --> 00:12:54.670
After going inside, do as I told you.

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:56.870
Deal with her properly.

00:12:57.360 --> 00:12:58.320
Don't worry.

00:12:58.790 --> 00:13:00.750
I'll make her

00:13:00.960 --> 00:13:02.400
enjoy herself.

00:13:27.240 --> 00:13:28.240
Who are you?

00:13:30.600 --> 00:13:31.440
Don't come over.

00:13:35.150 --> 00:13:35.990
Don't come over.

00:13:37.120 --> 00:13:37.960
Don't come over.

00:13:38.360 --> 00:13:39.200
Don't come over.

00:13:40.440 --> 00:13:41.280
Don't come over.

00:13:42.510 --> 00:13:43.510
You filthy woman.

00:13:46.510 --> 00:13:47.630
Don't come over.

00:13:52.780 --> 00:13:58.940
(9th lifetime,
Stabbed to death by Ruoli)

00:14:03.480 --> 00:14:04.960
Mr. Huo, bad news.

00:14:05.270 --> 00:14:06.270
Miss Jiang...

00:14:09.000 --> 00:14:09.840
Help!

00:14:10.600 --> 00:14:11.440
Help!

00:14:13.320 --> 00:14:14.200
Go away!

00:14:16.750 --> 00:14:17.590
Help!

00:14:27.790 --> 00:14:28.630
Spare me.

00:14:29.630 --> 00:14:30.790
Despicable!

00:14:38.200 --> 00:14:39.040
Ruoli.

00:14:39.910 --> 00:14:41.030
The incense has a problem.

00:15:01.320 --> 00:15:02.226
Drink some water first.

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:05.840
Ruoli.

00:15:08.750 --> 00:15:09.630
Calm down.

00:15:10.200 --> 00:15:11.040
Help me.

00:15:16.150 --> 00:15:16.990
Calm down.

00:15:18.630 --> 00:15:19.470
Help me.

00:15:19.960 --> 00:15:20.800
How can I help you?

00:15:35.900 --> 00:15:40.180
(A month later, Jiang Mansion)

00:15:56.720 --> 00:15:58.440
- Milady.
- Milady, are you okay?

00:15:59.550 --> 00:16:00.390
Hey, Ruoli.

00:16:00.670 --> 00:16:01.720
What happened to you?

00:16:02.000 --> 00:16:02.960
Are you feeling unwell?

00:16:04.320 --> 00:16:05.160
Perhaps

00:16:06.030 --> 00:16:07.760
I ate something wrong.

00:16:09.390 --> 00:16:10.230
I'm fine.

00:16:10.600 --> 00:16:12.750
Wanyue, don't make a fuss.

00:16:13.320 --> 00:16:14.720
I'm just concerned about you.

00:16:15.390 --> 00:16:16.600
You are vomiting so badly.

00:16:16.600 --> 00:16:17.440
Milady.

00:16:17.960 --> 00:16:19.360
Could it be morning sickness?

00:16:20.630 --> 00:16:22.630
Jiang Wanyue, that's nonsense.

00:16:23.790 --> 00:16:24.630
Wanyue,

00:16:25.200 --> 00:16:26.120
don't speak nonsense.

00:16:26.960 --> 00:16:28.600
Father, look at Ruoli.

00:16:28.870 --> 00:16:29.960
Her face looks terrible,

00:16:30.320 --> 00:16:31.360
and she suddenly vomited.

00:16:32.420 --> 00:16:33.290
This...

00:16:33.320 --> 00:16:34.510
It's morning sickness.

00:16:35.270 --> 00:16:36.910
- You...
- Our family has always valued

00:16:36.910 --> 00:16:37.790
reputation above all.

00:16:38.150 --> 00:16:39.080
If Ruoli...

00:16:40.320 --> 00:16:42.030
That'd bring shame to the entire family.

00:16:43.240 --> 00:16:44.240
- Qiao, hurry.
- Milady.

00:16:44.240 --> 00:16:45.320
Go invite Physician Zhang.

00:16:45.490 --> 00:16:46.360
- You...
- Go.

00:16:46.360 --> 00:16:47.200
Yes, milady.

00:17:01.080 --> 00:17:02.069
Physician Zhang, tell us.

00:17:02.080 --> 00:17:03.240
Is Ruoli pregnant?

00:17:03.550 --> 00:17:04.680
Tell us the truth.

00:17:07.160 --> 00:17:08.200
Mr. Jiang,

00:17:08.310 --> 00:17:09.150
Lady Wanyue,

00:17:09.880 --> 00:17:12.110
Lady Ruoli's pulse
is smooth and flowing,

00:17:12.200 --> 00:17:13.446
like pearls rolling on a plate.

00:17:13.880 --> 00:17:15.880
This is indeed a pregnancy pulse.

00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:17.840
What did you say?

00:17:21.640 --> 00:17:23.030
(Jiang Ruoli,)

00:17:23.440 --> 00:17:24.750
(you are finished.)

00:17:47.310 --> 00:17:48.830
♪The dream shattered♪

00:17:49.190 --> 00:17:50.870
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

00:17:50.870 --> 00:17:52.510
♪Like a restless soul♪

00:17:53.390 --> 00:17:54.950
♪How vague♪

00:17:55.350 --> 00:17:56.870
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

00:17:56.870 --> 00:17:59.110
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

00:17:59.910 --> 00:18:02.510
♪Love and hate entwined♪

00:18:02.990 --> 00:18:05.830
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

00:18:06.470 --> 00:18:11.230
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

00:18:11.830 --> 00:18:13.350
♪When fate falls apart♪

00:18:13.750 --> 00:18:17.310
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

00:18:18.030 --> 00:18:19.590
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

00:18:19.990 --> 00:18:23.710
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

00:18:24.430 --> 00:18:27.270
♪Life after life♪

00:18:27.750 --> 00:18:30.430
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

00:18:31.070 --> 00:18:35.150
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

00:18:35.230 --> 00:18:38.270
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

00:18:38.430 --> 00:18:39.830
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

00:18:39.830 --> 00:18:42.950
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

00:18:43.030 --> 00:18:44.470
♪Now shatter apart♪

00:18:44.590 --> 00:18:48.350
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

00:18:49.070 --> 00:18:51.870
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

00:18:52.150 --> 00:18:54.990
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

00:18:55.310 --> 00:18:59.710
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

00:18:59.950 --> 00:19:02.870
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

00:19:02.990 --> 00:19:07.430
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

00:19:07.630 --> 00:19:13.350
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

00:19:13.790 --> 00:19:16.510
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

00:19:16.750 --> 00:19:19.470
♪Sober or indulge♪

00:19:19.910 --> 00:19:25.910
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪